      "span_text": "The temperature sensing range obtained in our system is between 20°C and 100°C, because of the limit of the column oven employed, and the measurement resolution achieved is 0.1°C. Because the CO 2 laserfabricated LPFG is stable at high temperatures,  our temperature sensor system has a potentially large measurement range."
